1.19
log
@Per POSIX, we now only require <sys/msg.h>, <sys/sem.h>, or <sys/shm.h>
@
text
@.\"	$OpenBSD: semget.2,v 1.18 2014/02/13 07:30:39 guenther Exp $
.\"	$NetBSD: semget.2,v 1.2 1997/03/27 08:20:41 mikel Exp $
